data.description: Great location, Turnkey income producer DUBLEX!!! 2 unit of 1/1. Super private. Both unit has own backyard. Just renovated a year ago. Both unit come with furnitures. All furnitures are one year old. Washer/dryer placed in a shed in backside of the house and shared by both unit. Live in one of the unit and rent the other one out to cover your mortgage and live for free or rent both for long term/mid term or short-term w/AirBnb for great income. GREAT DEAL TO START WITH FHA!!
